    dc:description "FIGURE 30. Distribution map of Hyrmophlaeba bellula (Philippi, 1865) (green circles), Hyrmophlaeba carbonifera (Angulo, 1971) (Philippi, 1865) (yellow circles), Hyrmophlaeba cuprofulgida (Angulo, 1971) (red circles), Hyrmophlaeba lurida (Rondani, 1868) (orange circles), Hyrmophlaeba maculipennis (Macquart, 1850) (blue circles), Hyrmophlaeba paraluctuosa (Angulo, 1971) (peach circles), Hyrmophlaeba pipistrella (Angulo 1971) (magenta circles), Hyrmophlaeba rubronigra Bernardi, 1977 (lead circles), and Hyrmophlaeba ruizi (Stuardo, 1936) (pink circles)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10150140/files/figure.png" ;
